name: MIMIC-EU [Minimal]
short_description: Creates an Atlas of anonymized Acute Care cases to demonstrate the INDICATE platform's capability for aggregating ICU datasets and developing clinically relevant AI algorithms.

name: Early Detection of Organ Failure [Minimal]
short_description: Focuses on developing and deploying machine learning models that predict organ failure using time series data for clinical evaluation.

name: Virtual Digital Twin of Mechanical Ventilation [Minimal]
short_description: Develops a virtual digital twin for critically ill patients requiring mechanical ventilation involving sequential hourly clinical decisions.

name: Prediction of Neonatal and Pediatric Sepsis [Minimal]
short_description: Validates the federated infrastructure for pediatric data access, specifically focusing on sepsis prediction in neonatal and pediatric populations.

name: Quality Benchmarking Dashboards [Minimal]
short_description: Demonstrates data sharing practices designed to support continuous improvement of clinical practice through quality benchmarking.

name: Grand Rounds Workspace [Minimal]
short_description: Develops a collaborative European platform for exchanging clinical data and knowledge with potential for real-time synoptic sharing.
